  "remarks": "JSC Central Research Institute ‘Burevestnik’ is a Russian arms industry company. During its existence (since 1970), the company developed around 400 different types of arms and military equipment. It is best known for producing the following arms: artillery installations for naval artillery AK-176, A-190; mobile Mortars (types 2B11, 2K32, 2C12, 2B25), howitzer 2C35 and others.",
